<ul>
<li>It reads the SQL file specified.</li>
<li>Establishes a secure connection to the database.</li>
<li>Executes the SQL script from the file.</li>
<li>Fetches courses taught by the instructor from the <code node=3D"[object=
 Object]">courses</code> table.</li>
<li>Displays the courses in an HTML table.</li>
</ul>
</li>
