t Object]">courses</code> table.</li>
<li>The <code node=3D"[object Object]">courses</code> table has columns <co=
de node=3D"[object Object]">course_id</code>, <code node=3D"[object Object]=
">course_name</code>, and <code node=3D"[object Object]">instructor</code>.=
</li>
